1. How to install angualar2 for project
    cd /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2
    sudo npm install -g @angular/cli
    ng new TheAbyss    
    
2. How to run app
    cd /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss 
    ng serve --port 4444

3. Reinstall
    cd /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss 
    sudo rm -rf node_modules
    sudo npm cache clean --force
    sudo npm install -g @angular/cli
    sudo npm install

4. Save file

    sudo wget  -P /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss/src/assets/static/fonts/ "https://cdn.theabyss.com/static/fonts/ubuntu-v11-latin_cyrillic-ext-regular.woff2"

5. Convert base64 to png
    base64 -d <<< "" > /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss/src/assets/static/image/image8.png

    background-image: url("assets/static/image/image8.png");

 /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss/src/assets/static/img/appstore-2.png

 /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss/src/assets/static/img/benefits.png

