5.Run with hostname

	ng serve --host 192.168.1.9 --port 4444  --public-host mytheabyss.thu --disableHostCheck true 



ng generate class Hero
ng generate component HeroForm

6. Create new component
	touch /home/fcode4/Documents/MyCode/TheAbyss-Angular2/TheAbyss/src/app/component/account.component.ts
